{"tid":1338204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生聽住！","createTime":"2019-07-21T12:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T12:49:40.000Z","uid":265734,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"08cbb450312a5e543e80ab9e8a3f2309f9091e3b","tid":1338204,"uid":265734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"知道你哋經濟能力有限，呢個幾月過海出嚟好大負擔，屋企人都唔會金援你地。<br />\n<br />\n發夢成日見到你哋係地鐵站買單程飛係度倒晒身上啲錢出嚟籌旗，幾想問點解唔用機頂啲散銀呀？我哋擺得喺度就係俾自己人用！定你哋覺得我哋唔係自己人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，自己帶水出嚟，但港島呢邊買水貴！飲完自己嘅，人哋派水你有需要就拎！！！唔好捱壞自己！！！唔好怕醜！！！<br />\n<br />\n手足們，見到中學生唔該強制將車飛散銀塞俾佢哋！大家坐埋一條船，唔好怕醜，有需要就講呀！！！"},{"pid":"c49a204463c5317c44bb0e1d03e9adcfd4d7ab78","tid":1338204,"uid":76632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:35:52.000Z","msg":"中學生、大學生們，現場物資/資金有需要拎，唔使怕醜，冇人會歧視你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"a3e482554711e75819ea12a200ad932e34c1645a","tid":1338204,"uid":281252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"學生係拍醜啲，現場手足見到記得塞俾佢地同佢地講可以拎，唔係佢地唔好意思架"},{"pid":"64521e4783b0d7f776592971680cf0255ffac677","tid":1338204,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd371c65b7392fd055946b0b1c58236a47042f5","tid":1338204,"uid":277235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"放得出嚟就係俾你地用！<br />\n你唔用又係益曬mtr架咋<br />\n同我用盡佢啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b066119cdd1b752921136135396f626a6d47a3","tid":1338204,"uid"